 I kong2, "Li2 kong2 e5 chin ho2, iau2-ku2 li2 chai goa2 si7 chit8 e5 u7 hak8-bun7 e5 lang5, tek-khak bo5 hoan7-tioh8 thai5-lang5 e5 choe7. U7-iaN2 goa2 si7 u7 hak8-bun7 e5 lang5, goa2 ji7-chap8-gou7 ni5 ku2 ti7 bou2 toa7-oh8 ka3-chheh, siu7 chin-toa7 e5 chun-keng3. Goa2 seng5-jin7 ti7 chit ji7-chap8-gou7 ni5 ku2 e5 lai7-bin7, goa2 chin chhut-lat8 chu2-tiuN bo5 Siong7-te3, goa2 ji7-chap8-gou7 ni5 ku2 liau7-li2 chit-keng oh8-tng5, mui2-ni5 u7 chit8 chheng lang5 choe3 goa2 e5 hak8-seng, goa2 long2 tui3 in kan-cheng3 u2-tiu7 bo5 Siong7-te3, ia7 bo5 thian-tong5 te7-gek8. Chit-e5 kiat-ko2 chin-chiaN3 kiaN lang5, in ui7 kek-beng7 i2-au7, goa2 tu2-tioh8 chin-choe7 hak8-seng, choe3 cheng2-cheng2 put-hoat e5 su7. Goa2 sou2 hoan7 e5 choe7, iau2 pi2 chit-e5 thai5-lang5 e5 khah tang7, in-ui7 goa2 u7 cheng3 tok8 ti7 in e5 sim, hai7 in e5 leng5-hun5, hou7 in piN3-choe3 thai5 lang5 e5, in hian7-si5 long2 teh choe3 phaiN2 e5 kang. Chit-e5 lang5 chi2-u7 pun2-sin thai5-lang5, chong2-si7 goa2 u7 lian5-lui7 choe7-choe7 lang5 hou7 in thai5 lang5. I hoe2-kai2 chiu7 i2-cheng5 e5 su7 thang tiau5-tit8, chong2-si7 goa2 long2 bo5 hoat thang pou2-kiu3, ia7 bo5 hoat tit thang chhu2-siau i2-cheng5 e5 heng5-tong7. Na7 siat-su2 Siong7-te3 sia3-bian2 goa2 e5 choe7, goa2 sou2 choe3 e5 kang iah8 iu5-goan5 chhin-chhiuN7 kiaN-hiaN5, kap si2 e5 he2 tit8-tit8 tou7. Chhin-chhiuN7 goa2 chit ho7 lang5 thai2-tho2 u7 hoat-tou7 thang chin2-kiu3?" 
 I kong2 soah aN3-thau5, chhui3-phoe2 long2 si7 bak8-sai2, eng7 chhiu2 ng bin7. Sian-siN thak8 Ia5-sou chio-hou choe7-jin5 e5 oe7 chin toa7 siaN, i liam5-piN koh peh khi2-lai5 kong2, "Go5-lo5-su piN3 kau3 chit khoan2, sit8-chai7 si7 tui3 goan2, goan2 ku7-choat8 Siong7-te3, sou2-i2 oe7 hoat-siN chit ho7 put-heng7 e5 su7. Goan2 u7 chhiuN2 lang5 e5 liong5-sim, ia7 u7 hou7 Go5-lo5-su peng2 to3-tiau3. Thoe3 goa2 ki5-to2!" Long2-chong2 e5 lang5 long2 lau5 bak8-sai2. Au7-lai5 i koh khi2-lai5 ki5-to2 kong2, "Siong7-te3 ah, siat-su2 Li2 si7 chin e5, kiu5 Li2 hian2-beng5 ti7 goa2! Na7 kheng2 lin5-bin2 goa2, kiu5 Li2 kin-a2-jit8 hou7 goa2 chai! Sia3-bian2 goa2 long2-chong2 e5 choe7." Hit-e5-hng, si5-kan siuN7-te2, bo5 tak8-lang5 u7 ki-hoe7 thang kong2 in e5 ke3-sit. Hit si5 chit-e5 chu2-li2 phou7 hit-e5 thai5 lang5 e5, nng7 lang5 hoaN-hi2 kau3 lau5 bak8-sai2. Keh e5-hng, i koh toa3 kui-pan e5 pit-giap8 seng saN-kap lai5, hou7 in che7 ti7 thau5-cheng5 liau5. Hit-e5-hng in u7 chhit lang5, thiaN in e5 sian-siN e5, chhe7-tioh8 Siong7-te3. 
