 An-se-mou5 e5 sun7-than3
 Chit8-pai2 goa2 teh-beh khi3 ti7 Lam5 Bi2-chiu, Ga5-te7-ma2-liap8. Po2 Sian-siN chhiaN2 goa2 tui3 kui2-na7 ui7 sin3 Chu2 e5 In3-te7-an lang5 kang2-lun7 kiu3 lang5 e5 hoat-tou7. Chit8 e5 lau7-lang5 mia5 kio3 An-se-mou5, che7 ti7 au7-piah e5 te7-si3 liau5, goa2 oat8 ke3-khi3 ka7 i kong2, "An-se-mou5, chhiaN2 li2 ka7 goa2 kong2, li2 kin-ni5-lai7 in2-chhoa7 joa7-choe7 lang5 lai5 bat Ia5-sou." (Hit-si5 si7 ji7-geh8 chap8-ji7 jit8) Lau7-lang5 e5 bin7 chhih loh8-khi3 kong2, "Ah! Sian-siN, chin-chio2." Goa2 mng7 kong2, "Joa7-choe7, chhiaN2 ka7 goa2 kong2." I in3 kong2, "Chi2-u7 saN-chap8." 
 Hit-ni5 e5 chhit-geh8 chhoe, goa2 chih-tioh8 An-se-mou5 e5 phoe, phoe-lai7 liat8 chit8-pah si3-chap8-si3 e5 lang5-mia5, chiu7 si7 An-se-mou5 ti7 7 geh8 i2-cheng5 sou2 in2-chhoa7 lai5 kui Chu2 e5 lang5. Thang kong2 ti7 kau3-hoe7 choe3 kang e5, han2-tit u7 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni e5, iah8 thang kong2 chit8-si3 lang5 choe3 kiu3 lang5 e5 kang e5, An-se-mou5 si7 te7-it ho2 e5 chit8 e5. 
