 Tai7-piau2 “Sin5 e5 lang5." (II Liat8 4: 22) 
 Goa2 u7 chit8 e5 peng5-iu2, bat siu7 Bi2-kok cheng3-hu2 phai3 choe3 khi3 goa7-kok e5 tai7-piau2. Khi3 bo5 joa7-ku2, i u7 to3-lai5, goa2 mng7 i kong2, "Li2 siaN2-su7 to3-lai5?" I in3 kong2, "In-ui7 goa2 m7-ai3 koh tam-tng hit khoan2 e5 chek-seng5 lah." Goa2 mng7, "He si7 chaiN2-iuN7?" I kong2, "Goa2 bo5-lun7 khi3 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7, hia e5 peh-siN3 tit8-tit8 khoaN3 goa2, koh kio3 goa2, 'Uncle Sam'. (i3-su3 si7 chi2 Bi2-kok) Lian5 goa2 chi2-u7 teh lim-chui2 na7-tiaN7, in iah8 ui5-teh khoaN3, kong2 si7 Bi2-kok khoan2 e5 lim-chui2. Sou2-i2 goa2 m7-ai3 koh tam hit ho7 chek-seng5." 
 Lan2 choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2 si7 tu2-tu2 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni, se3-kan lang5 beh tit8-tit8 khoaN3 lan2, tit8-tit8 gi7-lun7 lan2. In bo5 beh chu3-i3 lan2 sou2 gim5 e5 si, lan2 e5 ki5-to2 a2-si7 lan2 e5 sin3-tiau5. In te7-it chu3-i3 e5, chiu7-si7 lan2 e5 kiaN5-choe3. 
 Heng5 sou2 khiam3 e5. I in3 kong2, "Long2 peng5-an." (II Liat8-ong5 4: 26) 
